      • runSingleStep

        public void runSingleStep()
                   throws Exception,
                          epanet.core.EpanetException
        Execute a only step (iteration) of algorithm for call. It method is used by GUI because let cancel the execution.

        Notes:
        Using this method you can't rerun the algorithm. If rerun the algorithm is needed you have to create a new algorithm instance.
        Specified by:
        runSingleStep in interface Algorithm<S extends Solution<?>>
        Throws:
        Exception - if are a problem in close of resources open in problem
        epanet.core.EpanetException - if there is a error in the simulation
